{
  "stem": "10572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Frank Shurman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-H-U-R-M-A-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fritz Schurmann.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was spelled S-C-H-U-- umlaut-- R-M-A-N-N.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "8th of January 1915.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "81.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Hildsheim, Germany.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "H-I-L-D-S-H-E-I-M.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived in a town of about 75,000, an old, old city with a 1,000-year history.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were-- lived in a middle-upper-class neighborhood in a beautiful home, three-story home with a beautiful garden outside of the walls of the old city, and we lived a very comfortable life.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a home, and as long as I can remember we always had kinder fraulein, a nanny and a maid.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every four weeks a wash-woman would come and do the big laundry and the ironing lady would come and do the ironing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father was [BACKGROUND NOISE] a very successful and very capable and very creative man in the men's fashion industry and respected as one of the leaders in this industry.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- were were-- we had friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our social life was part of our assimilated life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had many Jewish friends, but just as many Christian friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father was somewhere on the city council to supervise the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is like so that very old buildings would not be destroyed by people who wanted to do something to them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as I look back, my father was not just a highly respected man, but a very proud man who always made it very clear to everyone that he did what he did as a Jew, but as a German Jew and as a German.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If somebody would have asked me in 19-- before Hitler came to power, if some-- and maybe even after Hitler came to power, if somebody would have asked me, what's your nationality?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would-- I would have answered without any hesitation, I'm a German.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
